OL,3,CCardiff City and Leeds United pay
OL,4,Ctribute to former captain Sol Bamba
OL,6,FThousands of fans have paid tribute to
OL,7,FSol Bamba at Cardiff City Stadium
OL,8,Ffollowing the death of the former
OL,9,Fcaptain of Cardiff City and Leeds
OL,10,FUnited at the age of 39.
OL,12,FBamba passed away three weeks ago and,
OL,13,Fas fans gathered for his former teams
OL,14,Fto face each other on Saturday, they
OL,15,Fpaid tribute to him with cheers and
OL,16,Fapplause.
