OL,3,CCardiff City and Leeds United pay
OL,4,Ctribute to former captain Sol Bamba
OL,6,FFlowers, scarves, and football shirts
OL,7,Fwere laid at the statue of Fred Keenor
OL,8,Foutside the stadium to pay tribute to
OL,9,Fthe former captain of both teams
OL,10,Ffacing each other today.
OL,12,FInside the stadium, players from both
OL,13,Fteams took a moment to remember Bamba
OL,14,Fas fans in the crowd cheered and
OL,15,Fapplauded, holding up a banner which
OL,16,Fread, 'Sol Bamba, City legend.'
OL,18,FThe defender died age 39 while working
OL,19,Fas technical director at Turkish club
OL,20,FAdanaspor on August 31.
