OL,3,CCardiff City and Leeds United pay
OL,4,Ctribute to former captain Sol Bamba
OL,6,FA club statement said Bamba had fallen
OL,7,Fill before a match and was taken to
OL,8,Fhospital where he died.
OL,10,FHe made over 100 appearances for the
OL,11,FBluebirds in five years as a player
OL,12,Fand, in 2018, was part of the side
OL,13,Fwhich won promotion to the Premier
OL,14,FLeague.
OL,16,FBamba was diagnosed with Non-Hodgkin
OL,17,Flymphoma in 2021 while at Cardiff, but
OL,18,Fwas declared cancer-free after a
OL,19,Fcourse of chemotherapy and returned to
OL,20,Fplay again for the Bluebirds.
