OL,3,CCardiff City and Leeds United pay
OL,4,Ctribute to former captain Sol Bamba
OL,6,FLast week, a minute of applause was
OL,7,Forganised as Cardiff City took on
OL,8,FDerby County at Pride Park Stadium,
OL,9,FDerby.
OL,11,FBoth clubs wore black armbands for the
OL,12,Fgame, while fans could be heard
OL,13,Fsinging Wham's 'Last Christmas' in
OL,14,Ftribute to Bamba.
